{"tid":500622,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕老人~終身監禁~~","createTime":"2017-12-16T03:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T05:22:03.000Z","uid":27993,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b02c4e1e4af1851580cedd68c7bf0178e0dbba51","tid":500622,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:22:44.000Z","msg":"今日難得早起身咁緊係二話不說嘆返個早餐<br />\n係我手起刀落分雞屍既時候聽到<br />\n有個細路邊行邊跳唱:<br />\n聖誕老人 終身監禁<br />\n騎住鹿仔 去殺人<br />\n<br />\n估唔到依家嘅小朋友都仲係唱緊依啲<br />\n突然間好懷念 又覺得原來自己已經咁老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我見個細路咁可愛 皮膚仲滑住舊雞<br />\n於是就摸摸佢個頭 用慈祥既眼神望住佢<br />\n講咗句:<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><del>殺撚埋你呀</del></span></span>早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb5f761d556adc9161d94043d620ece83697ded","tid":500622,"uid":125756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:23:48.000Z","msg":"見到超人着底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b27c027b45b4df1a578c8f636f1210bd0ad176","tid":500622,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:24:49.000Z","msg":"我細個係唱見到超人賣底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6801d4ab973029f788e233f99a922666470f9d2","tid":500622,"uid":21696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:26:06.000Z","msg":"我個陣好似係<br />\n<br />\n見到靚女剝衫剝褲<br />\n見到超人賣底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aac7051ef725f22ca068a5284b7505d065cf55f","tid":500622,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:22:03.000Z","msg":"好多version全部都無厘頭<br />\n但細個又會跟住唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}